	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "7"
	"message" "None of this means anything anymore. But no one knows what happens when we turn it off. Maybe well wake up in Aperture Science. Maybe in Arkhey. Or maybe were already dead, and this is the last dream..."
